<XMLDocContent PageName="cobalt.logging.LogManager.IsLogSeverityEnabled" Title="IsLogSeverityEnabled method" xmlns="http://www.cobaltrenderer.com/schema/XMLDocSchema.xsd">
  <Paragraph>
    <PageRef PageName="cobalt.logging.Welcome">Home</PageRef> ->
    <PageRef PageName="cobalt.logging.LogManager">LogManager</PageRef> ->
    IsLogSeverityEnabled
  </Paragraph>
  <Section Title="Description">
    <Paragraph>
      The <TypeRef>IsLogSeverityEnabled</TypeRef> method reports whether a severity passes the manager-level filter.
    </Paragraph>
    <Note Type="Important">
      <Paragraph>
        This method checks only the manager-level filter. It does not inspect whether any log targets are currently registered.
      </Paragraph>
    </Note>
  </Section>
  <Section Title="Usage">
    <Code Language="C++"><![CDATA[bool IsLogSeverityEnabled(ILogger::Severity severity) const;]]></Code>
    <SubSection Title="Argument list">
      <ArgumentList>
        <ArgumentListEntry Type="Severity!cobalt.logging.ILogger.Severity" Name="severity">The severity value to test.</ArgumentListEntry>
      </ArgumentList>
    </SubSection>
    <SubSection Title="Return value">
      <ReturnValue Type="bool">
        <TypeRef>true</TypeRef> if the severity passes the manager-level filter; otherwise <TypeRef>false</TypeRef>.
      </ReturnValue>
    </SubSection>
  </Section>
  <Section Title="See also">
    <PageRefList>
      <PageRefListEntry PageName="cobalt.logging.ILogger.IsLogSeverityEnabled">ILogger.IsLogSeverityEnabled</PageRefListEntry>
      <PageRefListEntry PageName="cobalt.logging.LogManager.SetIncludeSeverity">LogManager.SetIncludeSeverity</PageRefListEntry>
    </PageRefList>
  </Section>
</XMLDocContent>
